			"name": "createCustomer",
			"description": "Create a customer in NetSuite. Use 'T' or 'F' in isperson to state if is a person or company. Use 'T' in isperson field to state this is a person or 'F' if it a company. In case it's a company, the company name is mandatory. In case it's a person, firstname and lastname are mandatory",
